# MLDS — Prototype Token Source of Truth

> **What this file is:** The canonical CSS token sheet exported from the MLDS Figma "Color-Tokens" and "Typography" pages. This file overrides the React Prototype Token Map in `MLDS-4_0-Reference.mdc` for any prototype font, color, radius, spacing, shadow, and motion value. When the two disagree, **this file wins for prototype work**.
>
> **When to use which file:**
> - **Building prototypes (`.canvas.tsx`, `.canvas.jsx`, any rendered React/HTML)** → use the tokens in this file
> - **Design audits, copy reviews, component specs, written design recommendations** → MLDS-4.0 reference still applies
>
> **Source:** MLDS Figma "Color-Tokens" + "Typography" pages, exported as `colors_and_type.css`. Real Baton Turbo `.otf` foundry files ship alongside the CSS in `/fonts/`.

---

## Critical change from MLDS-4.0 reference

| Topic | Old guidance (MLDS-4.0 reference) | **Now (this file)** |
|---|---|---|
| Font family | `'DM Sans', -apple-system, system-ui, sans-serif` (substitute, because Baton Turbo wasn't web-accessible) | **Baton Turbo** via `@font-face` (Book/Regular/Medium/Bold/Heavy) with the same fallback stack |
| Teal-700 | `#00B89D` | `#1EBABA` |
| Teal-800 | `#098669` | `#11937E` |
| Teal-1000 | `#072C28` | `#05332C` |
| Red-500 | `#FF334E` | `#FF5E57` |
| Yellow-500 | `#FFE11F` | `#FFDD59` |
| Radius scale | `--radius-xs: 8px` etc. | New scale: `--ml-radius-xs: 4px`, `sm: 8px`, `md: 14px`, `lg: 20px`, `xl: 24px`, `2xl: 40px`, `pill: 9999px` |
| Spacing | 8pt grid | 4pt grid (`--ml-space-1: 4px` … `--ml-space-20: 80px`) |
| Type scale | Mobile-first overrides at <480px | Mobile defaults baked in. Desktop scales up at ≥1024px (handled in production CSS, not the prototype) |

Existing prototypes built against MLDS-4.0 values do not need to be retroactively migrated. Apply this rule to all **new** prototype work and any active iteration.

