## Setup for Vite prototype apps (`cashflow-prototype/`)

1. Copy the Baton Turbo `.otf` files to `cashflow-prototype/public/fonts/` (they live at `/Users/jaf.jaffaizal/Desktop/🦁/00 AI/MoneyLion Design System/fonts/`).
2. Drop the full `colors_and_type.css` into `cashflow-prototype/src/styles/mlds-tokens.css`.
3. Import once at the entry: `import './styles/mlds-tokens.css'` in `src/main.tsx`.
4. In inline-style components, reference tokens via `var(--ml-*)` strings or a typed JS object that mirrors the tokens (see `T = { ... }` pattern at the top of `prototypes/CashFlowV2Draft.canvas.tsx`).

If the font files cannot be bundled (e.g., a stakeholder-facing artifact must be portable), fall back to `'DM Sans', -apple-system, system-ui, sans-serif` and explicitly note the substitution under the artifact.

